  overviewTitle="Straight teeth. No brackets. No wires."
  overviewText="Invisalign works through a series of custom clear plastic aligners, each slightly different from the last, that progressively shift your teeth into alignment. Every set is worn for about two weeks before advancing to the next. Because the aligners are removable, there are no food restrictions, brushing and flossing remain completely normal, and no one around you needs to know you're in orthodontic treatment."
  overviewExtra="As an Invisalign Gold Plus Provider, Thrive Dental has completed more Invisalign cases than the vast majority of practices in Queens — which means we have the clinical experience to handle everything from simple crowding corrections to complex bite issues. Patients from Bayside, Whitestone, Fresh Meadows, Little Neck, and Douglaston choose us for Invisalign because our team uses the iTero intraoral scanner for your initial scan — no messy putty, just a 3D digital model of your teeth built in minutes. The iTero's Outcome Simulator can actually show you what your teeth will look like after treatment before you commit. If you've been thinking about straightening your teeth but don't want braces, Invisalign at our Bayside practice is worth a conversation."
